item.title: New Site Who This
item.description: Secret Hidden Level 1 Header This is my first post. Enjoy! Part 1: Joke’s on you Joke’s on you, this isn’t my first rodeo with static site generators and as an experienced beginner level experimenter, I have a few complaints about static site generators. I mean, why not have your first post be a complaint? First, some history. So, at one point in time at some point in time last year (2017) or so, I read somewhere that it was a great idea to showcase yourself by having a personal website as like a part-CV part experience point of reference.
